<head>
	<link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Ubuntu' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
</head>
<div class ="container">
	<div class="fqTypeface">
		<div class="row-fluid">
			<div class ="span12">
				<h1><span class="logoTypeface">
					filmquotra</span><span class="fqAsterisk">*</span></h1>
				<div id="f"></div>
			</div>
			<div class ="span12">
				<h1><span class="fqEmphasis">
				film finance </span>isn't a dirty word.<span class="fqAsterisk">*</span></h1>
				</br>
				<h4 class="butWereAfraid"><span class="fqAsterisk">*</span>
				but you could have fooled us.</h4>
			</div><!--span12-->
		</div><!--row-fluid-->
		<div class="row-fluid">		
			<div class="span4">	
				<p>
				You’re a creative, passionate filmmaker. Your project is your life. But you want to learn more about the business side of things.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="span4">
				<ul class="asteriskList">
					<li>You ask a studio executive.  He makes you feel stupid.</li>
					<li>You ask your lawyer.  She’s dismissive.</li>
					<li>You ask a banker.  Doesn’t even respond.</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="span4">
				<p>
				We’re a group of film finance experts and technology geeks who've experienced your pain of getting a film project completed.  We know the risks and the heartache you face  We know how tough it is to get real information in a notoriously tight-lipped community. There’s a better way, and we think we’ve found it.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div> <!--row-fluid-->
	</div><!--fqTypeface-->

		<div class ="span6">	
			<div id="splashRegister">
				 <div id="registerbox">            
						<form class="form-vertical" id="registerform" method="POST" action="/register">
							<p>Sign Up</p>
							<div class="control-group">
								<div class="controls">
									<div class="input-prepend">
										<span class="add-on"><i class="icon-user"></i></span><input type="text" placeholder="Username" name="username" id="regUsername" autocomplete="Off" />
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="control-group">
								<div class="controls">
									<div class="input-prepend">
										<span class="add-on"><i class="icon-envelope"></i></span><input type="text" placeholder="Email" name="userid" id="regUserid" autocomplete="Off" />
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="control-group">
								<div class="controls">
									<div class="input-prepend">
										<span class="add-on"><i class="icon-lock"></i></span><input type="password" placeholder="Password" name="passwd" id="regPasswd" autocomplete="Off" />
									</div>
								</div>
					
							<div class="control-group">
								<span class="pull-left"><div class="btn btn-success"><%= link_to "Register", myslate_create_path %></div></span>
							</div>		
						</form>
				</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
